annotationA: Autophagy-related 7 is an E1-type ligase for the autophagic ubiquitin-like proteins Atg8a and Atg12. Its roles include autophagosome formation, maintaining neuromuscular function and normal lifespan
annotationB: Autophagy-related 18b, isoform A; Phosphatidylinositol-3,5-bisphosphate binding; phosphatidylinositol-3-phosphate binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: cellular response to oxidative stress; autophagic vacuole assembly
